name: Exuberance No. 5 Red Sparklers
description: Cosmos smiles deeply on Exuberance No. 5 Red Sparklers with inspirational Alizarin Crimson and dash of Cobalt Teal. Exuberance No. 5 Red Sparklers is a one-of-a-kind artistic collaboration that intertwines Tery Spataro's flower photographs and the artificial intelligence of Playform.io to give life to this transfixing new creation. The Exuberance art series are physical surface designs.
